      "id": "jbtt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 338,
      "y": 158,
      "width": 364,
      "height": 324,
      "text": "JOB  build-and-test           runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n\n1  actions/checkout@v4\n2  actions/setup-node@v4  (node 20, npm cache)\n3  npm ci            (backend dependencies)\n4  npm test          (jest)   ◀ GATE: fail = stop\n5  docker build      frontend + backend\n      tag = ${{ github.sha }}   (never :latest)\n6  docker save / metadata → next jobs",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "jbt",
      "originalText": "JOB  build-and-test           runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n\n1  actions/checkout@v4\n2  actions/setup-node@v4  (node 20, npm cache)\n3  npm ci            (backend dependencies)\n4  npm test          (jest)   ◀ GATE: fail = stop\n5  docker build      frontend + backend\n      tag = ${{ github.sha }}   (never :latest)\n6  docker save / metadata → next jobs",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 13
    },
